                      "name": "Rich Text Editor",
                      "text": "<h2>Entry Requirements</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>At least five GCSEs at grade C/4 or above including English Language or Maths. If your English Language is a D/3, your Maths must be at least a C/4 and vice versa</li>\n</ul>\n<p>or</p>\n<ul>\n<li>A Level 2 BTEC Diploma or above and GCSE English Language or Maths at grade C/4 or above</li>\n<li>Grade C/4 or above in an Art, Design or Media based GCSE is preferred</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em>Students will be required to present a portfolio or sketchbook of art work as part of the interview process to demonstrate commitment and potential.</em></p>",
