                {
                  "value": {
                    "dtgeContentTypeAlias": "widgetRTE",
                    "value": {
                      "name": "Rich Text Editor",
                      "text": "<h2>What could I do next?</h2>\n<p>You could progress to the Art Foundation Diploma or HND at USP College, or continue to university to study a range of design related qualifications.</p>\n<p>You could also progress directly to employment, in areas such as: Graphics, Advertising, Editorial, Fashion, Textiles, Publishing or Print.</p>\n<p>Future careers in design include Graphic Designer, Interior Design, Illustration, Visual Merchandising, Set Design and Fashion Promotion amongst many other routes.</p>",
